race.description: Barnson Tamworth Showcase Super Maiden Plate
race.comment: EAGLETURN (3) lightly raced gelding resuming after showing a ton of ability in his first preparation. Fitted with the two solid trials and expected to go close from the barrier. SIRAGUSA (10) three-year-old gelding by I Am Invincible out of Diamond Solitaire on debut for the Archibald yard. Given the three solid trials and he finds a winnable race. OUR BOY TOM (6) resumes. Only had the one run last prep when a plugging second over 1200m at Tamworth last November. Maps well with the trial win over 950m and can figure prominently. ALREADY BLUE (1) blinkers go on for this after disappointing when eighth over 1000m at Taree. Finds an easier race and expected to improve sharply.
